About us
Where Great Food, Cold Drinks, and Game Day Spirit Come Together
Home
About us
About us
Your Favorite Sports Grill Restaurant for More Than 25 Years
Located at the Best Western Gateway Grand Hotel and Conference Center, Gators Den Sports Grill has been a longstanding favorite with Gainesville locals and guests who want a welcoming place to eat and watch a game.
With the mission of providing fantastic service and delicious food and embracing the spirit of friendly competition, we’re the place to be regardless of who you’re rooting for.
About us
Drinks, Food, and Fun
Featuring a full bar with craft cocktails, local draft beers, and a popular wine selection, we’re also a great place to enjoy a quality drink. Our whiskey, tequila, and rum selection is constantly expanding to provide our guests with a variety of options, new and old.
With enough space to comfortably seat 60 patrons, Gators Den Sports Grill stands out as the favorite sports grill in Gainesville, FL.
